itemDescription: British general practitioner and professor of e-health and primary care

wikipedia_page.main: Elizabeth Murray  is a British general practitioner and professor of e-health and primary care at University College London. In 2003 she established the eHealth Unit at UCL where she is co-director, and she is also Deputy Director of the UCL Institute of Healthcare Engineering.
